본 file 은 disease-axis-orthogonal roadmap. hexa-bio 의 5 axis 가 hepatology (liver disease) 에 어떻게 기여하는지 cross-axis mapping + 신규 약물 기준 falsifier inventory.

(Distinct from `.roadmap.disease_gastrointestinal` — GI 는 gut / IBD / motility / pancreas 중심; hepatology 는 hepatocyte / cholangiocyte / portal system / hepatic immunology 전담. 2024 Rezdiffra approval 이후 NASH/MASH = first-in-class drug class 의 약물 표적 경관 변화.)

scope:
- MASLD / MASH (formerly NAFLD / NASH)
- viral hepatitis B (HBV chronic — functional cure target)
- viral hepatitis C (HCV — DAA era 거의 cure)
- viral hepatitis D (HDV — bulevirtide 2023 EMA / FDA pending)
- alcohol-associated liver disease (ALD)
- primary biliary cholangitis (PBC)
- primary sclerosing cholangitis (PSC)
- autoimmune hepatitis (AIH — cross-link `.roadmap.disease_autoimmune`)
- cirrhosis + portal hypertension
- hepatocellular carcinoma (HCC — cross-link `.roadmap.disease_cancer`)
- hepatorenal syndrome (HRS — cross-link `.roadmap.disease_renal`)
