- hereditary hemochromatosis (iron overload — cross-link `.roadmap.disease_toxicology`)
- α1-antitrypsin deficiency (AATD — cross-link `.roadmap.disease_pediatric_rare`)
- drug-induced liver injury (DILI — cross-link `.roadmap.disease_toxicology`)

